    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Xorg VMware Driver</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Xorg VMware Driver</application> package contains the X.Org
        Video Driver for VMware SVGA virtual video cards.
      </para>

      &lfs82_built;

